Professional Workshop Series

The workshop series aims to organize and host 2 to 3 workshops every year, hosted online, and freely available to everyone.

All workshops will be recorded and the videos will be available in their specific pages.


Past and Upcoming workshops

Navigating the workshops

Latest workshops are shown at the top by default.

Users can use the following to narrow their search for a workshop.

  • Categories: Search for keywords to find similar workshops
  • Filter: Filter the workshops by matching words in their titles or date
